            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Mercu<supplied reason="lost">rio</supplied> <lb n="2"/>aram <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>ecimus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Pris<lb break="no" n="4"/>cinus ex v<lb break="no" n="5"/>oto suscepto <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Mittelteil eines Altars. Z. 5: E klein in den Bogen des C eingeschrieben. Z. 6: das M ist zentriert und schneidet die untere Profilierung des Inschriftenfeldes.</p>
            </div>
